column5: Is this a good area to do some river fishing for steelie's? Typically I go to Manitoulin, but I dont' see why Parry Sound wouldn't be a good spot. Lot's of nice looking spots from a google earth perspective!  Pm if you like.  Cheers
Depends how many escape E's you can find...

we got some farmees from manitoulin last year, apparently there was a big release last spring.  I'd assume there are steelhead runs in this p sound area, I don't see how this section of the lake wouldn't have runs, unless I'm missing something. Next time I'm out there I'll ask some locals/
